ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, this course serves a good foundation for those students who wanna go further in pure maths and statistics.
It is a very good course. If you are interested in analysis or want to learn more tricks about proofs, you should take this course.
I would recommend it to students majored in math not in electrical engineering.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I learned more tricks about proving things, which is really helpful for doing research in control theory.
